               <p>I am a <rs id="t17891209-117-viclabel556" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891209-117-victim1067 t17891209-117-viclabel556"></join> at <placeName id="t17891209-117-crimeloc557">Isleworth</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17891209-117-crimeloc557" type="placeName" value="Isleworth"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17891209-117-crimeloc557" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891209-117-off555 t17891209-117-crimeloc557"></join>; on the 10th of October last, I missed a pick-ax and a copper pot; I went to 
               <persName id="t17891209-117-person1069">
                  James
                   Lover
               <interp inst="t17891209-117-person1069" type="surname" value="Lover"></interp>
