                     <interp inst="t17891209-117-person1069" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's at Isleworth; and there I found my pick-axe, and I discovered my copper pot at Richard Richardson's, at Brentford; and the persons who bought them, said they had them of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17891209-117-person1070">
                  JAMES
                   LOVER
