               <p>I purchased the pick-ax of the prisoner at the bar.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to by Mr. Bounce.)</p>
               <p>I gave one shilling and sixpence for it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17891209-117-person1071">
                  RICHARD
                   RICHARDSON
               <interp inst="t17891209-117-person1071" type="surname" value="RICHARDSON"></interp>
