                     <interp inst="t17891209-117-person1072" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw a copper pot in the possession of the prisoner, between eleven and twelve o'clock, in the month of October, on a Saturday, about three yards from Richardson's shop, and was by the side of him, and saw him go into Mr. Richardson's shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17891209-117-verdict558" type="verdictDescription">
